Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:11.06,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}誇りのBullet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.36,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Break you down Break you down Break you down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:22.25,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}拳放つ 聖なるヴィジョン Stand Proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:28.49,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百年沉睡的苏醒在召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:35.05,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星尘遥呼 相继汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:39.92,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男子汉一行已启程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:45.55,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏上穿越时间的沙漠之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.68,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宿命 如同一串错综连横的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:57.90,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挥起白金斩断命运
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.95,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迸射而出的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:11.06,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是高傲的弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:22.25,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铁拳百裂 神圣的幻象 Stand Proud!
